Package gobblin.yarn.event

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationReportArrivalEvent
    A type of events for the arrival of an ApplicationReport to be used with a EventBus.
    ContainerShutdownRequest
    A type of events for container shutdown requests to be used with a EventBus.
    DelegationTokenUpdatedEvent
    A dummy class representing a type of events fired when the delegation token has been updated by the controller.
    GetApplicationReportFailureEvent
    A type of events posted when the GobblinYarnAppLauncher fails to get the ApplicationReport of the Gobblin Yarn application.
    NewContainerRequest
    A type of events for new container requests to be used with a EventBus.
